headline: Wisconsin Families to Receive New Homes Through Assurant, CNH, and Local Habitat for Humanity Partnership
summary: RACINE, Wis., August 25, 2025--Assurant, Inc. (NYSE: AIZ), through the Assurant Foundation, and CNH (NYSE: CNH), a world-class equipment, technology and services company, are partnering for the third consecutive year with Habitat for Humanity of Racine & Kenosha Counties to help build two new homes for Racine families, helping them realize the dream of homeownership. This latest project will bring the partners’ total to six homes built for deserving community families since 2021.
